definition: surname Chen/Chen (c. 1045 - 479 BC), a Zhou dynasty state/Chen (557-589), one of the Southern Dynasties 南朝[Nan2 Chao2]
to lay out/to exhibit/to display/to narrate/to state/to explain/to tell/old/stale

sentences.english: The fifth is Old-type News Facts.
For example: R1 service door upper guide and door latch on doorframe is worn.
sentences.chinese: R1服務門上導軌和門框的門閂陳舊並且磨損。

sentences.english: Confined to a stale, ill-at-ease room.
sentences.chinese: 囿於一個陳舊的，拘束的空間。

sentences.english: The bread can be fresh or stale and crusts can be left on or removed.
sentences.chinese: 麪包可新鮮或陳舊的和結殼可以留在或刪除。

sentences.english: On pathological evaluation most of hematomas were old and organized.
sentences.chinese: 病理顯示血腫多爲陳舊性和機化。

sentences.english: There was a smell of cheap soap and of ancient hair-oil in the room.
sentences.chinese: 房間裏有一股劣質肥皂和陳舊髮油的氣味。

sentences.english: She said that Jane's new coat was old-fashioned and not worth the money she had paid for it.
sentences.chinese: 她說簡的新大衣式樣陳舊，不值得她付出的錢。

sentences.english: I can listen to many old but famous songs.
sentences.chinese: 我可以聽到一些陳舊但是很有名的歌曲。

sentences.english: Objective To sum up the results of the treatment of old Achilles tendon rupture repaired by the fascia lata transplantation.
sentences.chinese: 目的總結采用闊筋膜移植治療陳舊性跟腱斷裂的療效。

sentences.english: I'm tired of the old thing anyway. I'll make a better one.
sentences.chinese: 那些陳舊的東西讓我煩透了，我能做的更好。

sentences.english: In Brarizonail- many long lost forests are quite well preserves.
sentences.chinese: 在巴西，陳舊的森林生存十分周備。

sentences.english: This book was old and soon fell apart.
sentences.chinese: 這本書太陳舊了，很快就破碎了。

sentences.english: We endeavour to avoid the old, romantic idea of a gusher .
sentences.chinese: 我們力求避免那種陳舊的，富有浪漫色彩的噴油方式。

sentences.english: That part of the palace was very old, and there were very few people there.
sentences.chinese: 宮樓已經十分的陳舊了，幾乎沒有什麼人。

sentences.english: The last reason - the problem of regime.
sentences.chinese: 最後是陳舊體制的原因。

sentences.english: The tarp hangs from a barbwire fence which surrounds an abandoned, old compound.
sentences.chinese: 篷布掛在柵欄上，圈起一塊廢棄陳舊的場地。
